Deprecated. using "Raw" MapReduce over Kiji tables is no longer the preferred mechanism for iterating over rows of a Kiji table. To write a function that processes and updates a table in a row-by-row fashion, you should extend org.kiji.mapreduce.produce.KijiProducer. You should use org.kiji.mapreduce.produce.KijiProduceJobBuilder for constructing such MapReduce jobs.
